<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 22 at 2:57AM EDT  by NWS Boston</headline>
<description>...ELEVATED FIRE WEATHER POTENTIAL TODAY...
Sunny skies, gusty northwest winds between 25 to 30 mph and low
relative humidity values between 20 to 30 percent has raised
concerns about elevated fire weather potential today.
Open burning is not recommended today. Follow instructions of
local fire wardens. Be very careful when handling and disposing of
ignition sources outdoors, such as cigarettes or matches.</description>
